      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense math-wise but it still feels so counter-intuitive. it's like i'm fighting an uphill battle where the interest is basically working against every step i take. do you think there's any way to stop the interest from mounting like that, or is it just an unavoidable part of how these loans are designed to work?",
